Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這是關於你的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a story about you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也關於我和你的狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and me and your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之前  在狗出現之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was a time not long ago... before dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他們以前不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的狗有大有小 寵物狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now there are big ones, small ones, snugglers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,守護犬  獵犬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}guardians, hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,各式各樣的狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every kind of dog you could possibly want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅僅是狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,形形色色的各種生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did all the different kinds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都是從哪裏來的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of living creatures come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是來自能量的轉換  聽上去可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The answer is a transforming power that sounds like something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,像是童話或者神話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}straight out of a fairy tale or myth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但並非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's no such thing.
